    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://7xjiyb.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/blog_4_headimage.jpg?imageMogr2/crop/900x500" alt="image"><br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="����������ʲo����"><a href="#����������ʲo����" class="headerlink" title="����������ʲô����"></a>����������ʲô����</h2><p>����һ�����͵���Ŀ�������������ӡ���˾��������������������ô�������Ķ�������Ҳ�Ǻ������ġ�������Ҫ���������ڱ���������ʱ����ͬʱ�н��ü��̺����ü��̵Ĳ������������ܵ��ļ�����ʼ�ĵ������ǽ�����edittext�Ŀؼ�ʹ��ʱ�򣬱���������ʱ����Ҫ���õ����̵��Զ�����(�����Զ���������ͬ��������·�Ļ������ܻ���Щ���⣬��Ҫ���⴦��)<br>ͬʱ�����������ж���edittextʱ�������ܹ�ͳһ�����������ĵ��������̹��ܡ�</p><h2 id="�L��ʺ�����Щ����Ӧ��"><a href="#�L��ʺ�����Щ����Ӧ��" class="headerlink" title="�Ƚ��ʺ�����Щ����Ӧ��"></a>�Ƚ��ʺ�����Щ����Ӧ��</h2><p>�ü��������ڲ�Ʒ�ľ��峡����Ҳ������΢ժ������Ϊһ�����ÿؼ�ʹ�á�</p><h2 id="Դ���о�����"><a href="#Դ���о�����" class="headerlink" title="Դ���о�����"></a>Դ���о�����</h2><p>����������ʼ�϶�Ҫ�ȿ���edittext���������̻����Ĳ�����Դ�롣��edittext����textview���ҵ���<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/**</div><div class="line">* Sets whether the soft input method will be made visible when this  </div><div class="line"> * TextView gets focused. The default is true.  </div><div class="line"> */  </div><div class="line">@android.view.RemotableViewMethod  </div><div class="line">public final void setShowSoftInputOnFocus(boolean show) &#123;  </div><div class="line">    createEditorIfNeeded();  </div><div class="line">    mEditor.mShowSoftInputOnFocus = show;  </div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>���������Ρ�<br>����ֱ��ʹ�õ��÷��������е�ʱ������ʾ��<br>Call requires API level 21 (current min is 18): android.widget.TextView#setShowSoftInputOnFocus less…<br>android 18�汾���ϵĲ��ܹ���������������Ϊ�˼��ݵͰ汾��ͬʱ��֤�������ã��뵽���÷��������е��ã��������������쳣��  </p><h3 id="�����k������£�"><a href="#�����k������£�" class="headerlink" title="�����ķ������£�"></a>�����ķ������£�</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/**</div><div class="line">     * ��ֹEdittext���������̣�������Ȼ������ʾ��</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void disableShowSoftInput() &#123;</div><div class="line">        softinputSet(false);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * ����Edittext���������̣�������Ȼ������ʾ��</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void openShowSoftInput() &#123;</div><div class="line">        softinputSet(true);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    public void softinputSet(boolean isShow)&#123;</div><div class="line">        if (android.os.Build.VERSION.SDK_INT &lt;= 10) &#123;</div><div class="line">            this.setInputType(InputType.TYPE_NULL);</div><div class="line">        &#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line">            Class&lt;EditText&gt; cls = EditText.class;</div><div class="line">            Method method;</div><div class="line">            try &#123;</div><div class="line">                method = cls.getMethod(&quot;setShowSoftInputOnFocus&quot;, boolean.class);</div><div class="line">                method.setAccessible(true);</div><div class="line">                method.invoke(this, isShow);</div><div class="line">            &#125; catch (Exception e) &#123;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            try &#123;</div><div class="line">                method = cls.getMethod(&quot;setSoftInputShownOnFocus&quot;, boolean.class);</div><div class="line">                method.setAccessible(true);</div><div class="line">                method.invoke(this, isShow);</div><div class="line">            &#125; catch (Exception e) &#123;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>�������������������ĵ�������  </p><h3 id="�����еK����������L���Ч��ʵ��"><a href="#�����еK����������L���Ч��ʵ��" class="headerlink" title="�����еĶ����������Ľ���Ч��ʵ��"></a>�����еĶ����������Ľ���Ч��ʵ��</h3><p>ʵ���˵�����Ч������ô��Ҫʵ�ֶ�����������Ч������ʱ����Ӧ�þͿ��Դ��ſ���layout����������֧�֡�<br>��Ϊedittext�������̵����ܶ�ʱ�����Ƿ��н�������������ô��layout��ѡȡ��һ�����ֽ���֧�ֵ�ʱ�򣬿��Կ�����������viewgroup����focus��ʵ�ַ����Ϳ��Ʒ�����ֱ��ѡȡ��linearlayout�Ĳ����������о���<br>��������������������������view��ȥ��<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus to the previous selectable</div><div class="line">     * item.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_BACKWARD = 0x00000001;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus to the next selectable</div><div class="line">     * item.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_FORWARD = 0x00000002;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus to the left.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_LEFT = 0x00000011;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus up.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_UP = 0x00000021;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus to the right.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_RIGHT = 0x00000042;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * Use with &#123;@link #focusSearch(int)&#125;. Move focus down.</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public static final int FOCUS_DOWN = 0x00000082;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>view ������view��focus�ı�־�����ϼ��֣���־������view�Ľ����ı仯����ʱ�����ſ��Թ�עһ��focus_down�ˣ�����֪�⡣�����˹ٷ��ĵ�������Ҳ�����ˣ�������view���ҵ���һ�����Ի�ȡ������λ�á���ô�����Ϳ��Զ������ˡ�</p><h3 id="�����ж�����������Ч������"><a href="#�����ж�����������Ч������" class="headerlink" title="�����ж�����������Ч������"></a>�����ж�����������Ч������</h3><p>�ڲ������ҵ���ǰ�Ļ�ȡ��������view��ͬʱ������һ����view������������һ����viwe���ɡ�<br>ʵ�ִ��룺<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/**</div><div class="line">     * ��������ȥһ����������</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void next()&#123;</div><div class="line">        boolean isThis = false;</div><div class="line">        View current = this.findFocus();</div><div class="line">        ArrayList&lt;View&gt; views =  this.getFocusables(View.FOCUS_DOWN);</div><div class="line">        for(View view : views )&#123;</div><div class="line">            if(isThis)&#123;</div><div class="line">                isThis = false;</div><div class="line">                view.requestFocus();</div><div class="line">                return ;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">            if(current == view)&#123;</div><div class="line">                isThis = true;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * ��������ȥһ����������</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void previous()&#123;</div><div class="line">        View current = this.findFocus();</div><div class="line">        ArrayList&lt;View&gt; views =  this.getFocusables(View.FOCUS_DOWN);</div><div class="line">        for(int i = 0 ; i &lt; views.size(); i++)&#123;</div><div class="line">            if(current == views.get(i))&#123;</div><div class="line">                if(i &gt;= 1)&#123;</div><div class="line">                    views.get(i-1).requestFocus();</div><div class="line">                &#125;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * ������view���������Զ�����</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void forbidenAllChildSoftinput()&#123;</div><div class="line">        KeyBoardDisableEditText editText;</div><div class="line">        ArrayList&lt;View&gt; views =  this.getFocusables(View.FOCUS_DOWN);</div><div class="line">        for(View view : views)&#123;</div><div class="line">            if(view instanceof KeyBoardDisableEditText)&#123;</div><div class="line">                editText = (KeyBoardDisableEditText) view;</div><div class="line">                editText.disableShowSoftInput();</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    /**</div><div class="line">     * ������view���������Զ�����</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    public void startAllChildSoftinput()&#123;</div><div class="line">        KeyBoardDisableEditText editText;</div><div class="line">        ArrayList&lt;View&gt; views =  this.getFocusables(View.FOCUS_DOWN);</div><div class="line">        for(View view : views)&#123;</div><div class="line">            if(view instanceof KeyBoardDisableEditText)&#123;</div><div class="line">                editText = (KeyBoardDisableEditText) view;</div><div class="line">                editText.openShowSoftInput();</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>ͬʱ��layout�л�������һ�����Կ��Ʋ���������sorftinput�����¼��ķ�������ô���Ƶ������ǿ�����ȫ���������˵ġ�ԭ������ͨ��Դ��������һ��hack�������ѡ�<br>demo���������ȹҳ�����  </p><p><a href="https://github.com/Begin-With-Start/Demoall/blob/master/app/src/main/java/demo/minifly/com/map/KeyBoardEditText.java" target="_blank" rel="external">������֮������֮��</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/Begin-With-Start/Demoall/blob/master/app/src/main/java/demo/minifly/com/map/TextInputLayout.java" target="_blank" rel="external">������֮���ֿ��ƴ���֮��</a></p>]]></content>
    
